msgs.title: Thank you!
msgs.long: Thank you for installing The Toeic Full Test!

body.text: Thank you for installing Toeic Full Test!
Read the entire passage once very carefully (30 seconds per passage).
Then read a third time and without looking at the answer choices
The followings will be applied to the actual test
At the end of each question, it will automatically move to the next one and wil not be returnable.
Next question can be previewed by tapping on a 'Preview Next'.
Images can be zoomed in/out, moved arround, or opened in fullscreen.
Scores will be calculated after 'Submit' button is tapped.
Summitted tests can be reviewed (but answers are not changable) View History section on the home screen.
